    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total gem! This car has been meticulously cared for and is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just left the showroom floor. It\u2019s been garage-kept, never smoked in, and drives incredibly smooth. I\u2019m looking for a quick sale so I\u2019ve priced it to move, but I promise you won\u2019t find a cleaner ride out there. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 42950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
