      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul to ensure structural and mechanical longevity. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional lateral grip and corner-exit traction. The suspension remains true to its factory kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the original N\u00fcrburgring-tuned damping profile. This vehicle represents a turnkey acquisition for the discerning collector prioritizing mechanical purity and performance provenance.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
