    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade example that presents in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original deep-gloss factory finish with no evidence of swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. The exterior is protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating, ensuring the paint remains as vibrant as the day it left the assembly line. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the interior still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate climate controls, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has a comprehensive, documented service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is detailed to a concours-level standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting a life spent on dry roads and under a cover. It sits on original wheels wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber. This is not merely a used car; it is a meticulously curated piece of automotive history for the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. All original keys, manuals, and a thick binder of service receipts are included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
