      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve been super meticulous with it, and it drives like an absolute dream. You won\u2019t find a single blemish on it! If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new but without that brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I'd love for it to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
