      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S in concours-level condition. This 996.2 utilizes the 3.6L flat-six with Variocam Plus, paired with a 6-speed Getrag manual transaxle. The IMS bearing has been addressed via LN Engineering retrofit, and the rear main seal remains dry. The wide-body chassis features a viscous-clutch AWD system and factory-spec Bilstein dampers for optimal lateral grip. Performance is anchored by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors. With zero deferred maintenance and a pristine underbody, this is a definitive example for the technical purist.",
